{"tid":2252724,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"太古城2房則王1110萬元獲用家承接","createTime":"2020-10-21T15:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T02:23:47.000Z","uid":126442,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb07913684737c940034c19441d7f4b9ce8520d","tid":2252724,"uid":126442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"中原地產太古城東山閣分行高級分行經理莊劍嵐透露，太古城寶安閣中層F室，實用面積583平方呎，建築面積675平方呎，2房則王間隔，向西南，望公園景。業主於9月底以1180萬元放盤，最終獲區內用家以1110萬元承接，折合平均實用呎價19039元。<br />\n<br />\n莊劍嵐指，原業主於1990年2月以99萬元買入單位，持貨30年，帳面獲利1011萬元，期內單位升值超過10.2倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">持貨30年，帳面獲利1011萬元</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae9854f6254377d4ce80fe441fac770fbc72349","tid":2252724,"uid":19552,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"30年前港樓只係抽獎獎品<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/175451_c8b2dc94b2bcde92595d0df09e21297b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F175451_c8b2dc94b2bcde92595d0df09e21297b.png&h=6f7d4a2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"163760ed8858c2568e72a4901003fbba11d877cc","tid":2252724,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T16:05:36.000Z","msg":"單以數字來睇&nbsp;30年99萬&gt;1110萬<br />\n唔係話好特別<br />\n <br />\n同時期恒生指數都差不多升左十倍"},{"pid":"11e15efb68389151be90580beaf9beeb34a23eb7","tid":2252724,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ae9854f6254377d4ce80fe441fac770fbc72349","tid":2252724,"uid":19552,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"30年前港樓只係抽獎獎品<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/175451_c8b2dc94b2bcde92595d0df09e21297b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%